From 2044c70ff3b1b061d889d968796723c0cc192708 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Victor=20Pal=C3=A9ologue?= <victor.paleologue@palaio.eu>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 09:18:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Replace geometry_msgs/Pose2D with local Pose2D

geometry_msgs/Pose2D was deprecated and removed in ROS 2 Rolling, which broke
the build of naoqi_bridge_msgs there. Define a field-compatible
naoqi_bridge_msgs/Pose2D and use it in CmdPoseService so the package builds on
all active distros (Humble, Jazzy, Kilted, Rolling).
---
 msg/Pose2D.msg         | 6 ++++++
 srv/CmdPoseService.srv | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 7 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 msg/Pose2D.msg

diff --git a/msg/Pose2D.msg b/msg/Pose2D.msg
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..3a9dc80
--- /dev/null
+++ b/msg/Pose2D.msg
@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@
+# A 2D pose (x, y position and orientation theta), replacing geometry_msgs/Pose2D
+# which was deprecated and removed in ROS 2 Rolling. Field-compatible with the
+# original geometry_msgs/Pose2D.
+float64 x
+float64 y
+float64 theta
diff --git a/srv/CmdPoseService.srv b/srv/CmdPoseService.srv
index 046b863..e46eb1b 100644
--- a/srv/CmdPoseService.srv
+++ b/srv/CmdPoseService.srv
@@ -1,3 +1,3 @@
 # Command pose as service:
-geometry_msgs/Pose2D pose
+naoqi_bridge_msgs/Pose2D pose
 ---
-- 
